&lt;li&gt;Full time Veterinarian&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;New graduates seeking mentorship and experienced veterinarians welcome&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborative team member who keeps up to date on new developments in veterinary medicine&lt;/li&gt;
